text: Mutal () is a rural locality (a village) in Shabagishsky Selsoviet, Kuyurgazinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 4 as of 2010. There is 1 street.Карта Куюргазинского района Башкортостана == References == Category:Rural localities in Kuyurgazinsky District
title: Mutal, Republic of Bashkortostan
